Package honeywell.printer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Document
    This is the base class for the O'Neil printer document objects.
    DocumentDPL
    This class handles the interface between the printer and the user application that wishes to use an Datamax-O'Neil DPL printer.
    DocumentExPCL_LP
    This class is use to build a print job for ExPCL language, Line Print mode.
    DocumentExPCL_PP
    This class is use to build a print job for ExPCL language, Page Print mode.
    DocumentEZ
    This class handles the interface between the printer and the user application that wishes to use an Datamax-O'Neil printer.
    DocumentLP
    This class handles the interface between the printer and the user application that wishes to use an Datamax-O'Neil printer.
    Parameters
    This base class represents the general parameters that can be used to alter the printing characteristics when 'printing' to a Document object.
    ParametersDPL
    This class represents the general parameters that can be used to alter the printing characteristics when 'printing' to a DocumentDPL object.
    ParametersExPCL_LP
    This class represents the general parameters that can be used to alter the printing characteristics when 'printing' to a DocumentExPCL_PP object.
    ParametersExPCL_PP  
    ParametersEZ
    This class represents the general parameters that can be used to alter the printing characteristics when 'printing' to a DocumentEZ object.
    ParametersLP
    This class represents the general parameters that can be used to alter the printing characteristics when 'printing' to a DocumentLP object.
    UPSMessage
    Class containing UPS message for printing Maxicode Bar Codes
